{"tid":1194660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣相信反修例遊行人數超過03年七一遊行","createTime":"2019-06-09T10:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T10:59:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"22e48949121e385fc1fb1107ede14116f6cb9a0d","tid":1194660,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"民陣下午發起反對修訂《逃犯條例》遊行，遊行隊伍陸續抵達終點立法會大樓外，參與者繼續在現場舉行集會。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰在台上發言時表示，民陣要求行政長官林鄭月娥到場，面對市民。他又說，仍有遊行人士在起點等候出發，無法估算參與遊行的人數，相信港人已締造歷史，人數是超過2003年的七一遊行人數。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，對警方的安排感到非常失望，認為警方有一段時間準備遊行工作，但未有盡早開路給市民遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461714-20190609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461714-20190609.htm&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=be212166\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461714-20190609.htm&h=7ce9dba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461714-20190609.htm</a>"},{"pid":"66b7ad92434058c598919003b5abbafb72a4fb0c","tid":1194660,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"一定多過啦<br />\n<br />\n民陣唔好走去on99自己打七折"}]}